{"tid":2155880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邱騰華一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「邱騰華，你又搞港獨了！","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T15:09:58.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1406,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"16932d732845f4d1e84f15157bd40807e1752446","tid":2155880,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"邱騰華一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看着他笑，有的叫道，「邱騰華，你又搞港獨了！」他不回答，對櫃裏說，「放售物業，要現金。」便排出三個倫敦物業。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，「你一定又被人家加關稅！」邱騰華睜大眼睛說，「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白&hellip;&hellip;」「什麼清白？我前天親眼見你的出口貨物，貼著「中國製造」標籤。」邱騰華便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，「香港不能算中國&hellip;&hellip;香港製造！&hellip;&hellip;基本法賦予的事，能加稅麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「影響不大」，什麼「指白為黑」之類，引得眾人都鬨笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"65784dfb2596a0eb4406a115afe76568ba1def68","tid":2155880,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cfa4890ee8d0581708c66b6994e014cf13c770eb","tid":2155880,"uid":282930,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09395e07fa8e0e059cff1c2e95a9cadb6fe2f039","tid":2155880,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"459c2a6575528ee04cbb7197ec2db6f761cfe5a1","tid":2155880,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2282e9d42f